---
import '../styles/styles.scss';
---
<div class="label label-pork-n-beans">
  <header>
    <h1 class="bold">Nutrition Facts</h1>
    <h3 class="bold">(Campbell's Pork and Beans)</h3>
    <div class="divider "></div>
    <p>About 4.5 servings per container</p>
    <p class="bold">Serving size <span>1/2 cup (130g)</span></p>
  </header>
  <div class="divider large"></div>
  <div class="calories-info">
    <div class="left-container">
      <h2 class="bold small-text">Amount per serving</h2>
      <p>Calories</p>
    </div>
    <span>130</span>
  </div>
  <div class="divider medium"></div>
  <div class="wen-xin-ti-xing">
    <p class="bold">陽光檸檬茶 : <span>乜咁啱嘅？邊度都有陽光</span></p>
  </div>
  <div class="divider medium"></div>
  <div class="daily-value small-text">
    <p class="bold right no-divider">% Daily Value *</p>
    <div class="divider "></div>
    <p>
      <span><span class="bold">Total Fat</span> 0.5g</span>
      <span class="bold">1%</span>
    </p>
    <p class="indent no-divider">
      Saturated Fat 0g <span class="bold">0%</span>
    </p>
    <div class="divider "></div>
    <p class="indent no-divider"><span><i>Trans</i> Fat 0g</span></p>
    <div class="divider "></div>
    <p>
      <span>
        <span class="bold">Cholesterol</span> 0mg
      </span>
      <span class="bold">0%</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span><span class="bold">Sodium</span> 480mg</span>
      <span class="bold">21%</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span><span class="bold">Total Carbohydrates</span> 27g</span>
      <span class="bold">10%</span>
    </p>
    <p class="indent no-divider">
      <span>Dietary Fiber 6g</span>
      <span>21%</span>
    </p>
    <div class="divider "></div>
    <p class="indent no-divider">Total Sugars 9g</p>
    <div class="divider double-indent"></div>
    <p class="double-indent no-divider">
      Incl. 7g Added Sugars<span class="bold">14%</span>
      <div class="divider "></div>
    </p>
    <p class="no-divider"><span class="bold">Protein</span> 5g
      <div class="divider large"></div>
      <p>Vitamin D 0mg <span>0%</span></p>
      <p>Calcium 40mg <span>4%</span></p>
      <p>Iron 1.9mg <span>10%</span></p>
      <p class="no-divider">Potassium 270mg <span>6%</span></p>
    </p>
    <div class="divider medium"></div>
    <p class="note no-divider">
      * The % Daily Value (DV) tells you how much a nutrient in a serving of
      food contributes to a daily diet. 2,000 calories a day is used for
      general nutrition advice.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>